00:29:17.818 --> 00:29:19.734
together.
But, you could imagine a

00:29:19.734 --> 00:29:22.523
sufficiently big black hole,
kind of encompassing the whole

00:29:22.523 --> 00:29:24.880
Universe, that wouldn't affect
us in that way.

00:29:24.880 --> 00:29:29.299
So, it's not inconceivable.
Yeah?

00:29:29.299 --> 00:29:33.527
Student: [Inaudible]
Professor Charles

00:29:33.527 --> 00:29:37.665
Bailyn: Yeah,
