00:30:43.720 --> 00:30:48.395
from the center of the Earth.
And that's vastly more than the

00:30:48.395 --> 00:30:51.190
sum of all contributions by
stars.

00:30:51.190 --> 00:30:54.357
And it's vastly less than what
